    <h2>Introduction to HTML</h2>
    <p><span class="bold">HTML</span> (Hypertext Markup Language) is used to create documents on the <span class="underline">World Wide Web</span>. It is simply a collection of certain keywords called "<span class="bold">Tags</span>" that are helpful in writing the document to be displayed using a browser on the Internet. HTML was developed by <span class="bold">TIM BERNERS-LEE</span> in 1992.</p>

